decision we are for the decision he said 
but he said the decision did not apply to intraparty agreements 
and would not force likud to make public its pact with avraham 
sharir a former tourism minister who was lured back after crossing 
over to labor briefly 
labor party secretary micha harish was quoted by the jerusalem 
post as saying we will keep our promise to disclose details of 
coalition pacts 
