the victory over nazi germany and speakers addressing the crowd 
denounced the latvian parliaments declaration of independence on 
friday 
we consider the declaration of independence a defeat for 
everyone said lt gen oleg zinchenko head of the political 
directorate of the baltic military region which includes latvia 
lithuania and estonia 
