republics said yazov 
when latvia declared itself independence it did not ask for an 
immediate break with moscow or suspend the soviet constitution 
like estonia it has set an unspecified transition period for 
secession 
latvians are waiting to see if the kremlin will impose economic 
sanctions and send troops to occupy some government buildings as 
it did to lithuania after that republics independence decree 
unlike in lithuania where the population is 80 percent ethnic 
lithuanian ethnic latvians are in a bare majority in the republic 
