<TEXT>
the soviet union proudly paraded its military 
might through red square today marking the 45th anniversary of the 
defeat of nazi germany as kremlin leaders grapple with the 
reunification of their former foe 
world war ii veterans with red ribbons on their suits 
accompanied some of the tanks and artillery they fought with from 
