an interstate probe of computer hacking has 
uncovered losses that may reach millions of dollars and could be 
just the tip of the iceberg federal law enforcement officials 
said wednedsay 
no computercrime arrests resulted however when 27 search 
warrants served in a dozen cities were served by 150 secret service 
