each in chicago los angeles and pittsburgh were arrested for 
unrelated offenses officials said 
secret service officials declined to release any specifics 
including the number of people targeted saying the twoyear 
investigation codenamed operation sun devil was continuing 
the probe is focused on illegal entry into computer systems and 
