that the may 2 pleadings should kept under seal because they 
contain sensitive information 
blochs memorandum contains no classified information and 
filing it on the public record of this case would not harm the 
national security nor impede the underlying administrative 
proceeding being conducted by the state department the justice 
petition argued 
