away to cicero where they were welcomed by the school district and 
the community 
ryan lived the life of a normal teenager hanging out with 
friends dating his prom date for this year heather mcnew 
decided not to go to the dance after ryan died 
mrs white is trying to move forward her friends and family 
keep expecting her to wear out with all the activity especially 
answering the thousands of cards and letters she has received since 
ryans death but she believes she can stay strong 
she is planning a memorial day ceremony to mark her sons 
achievements at that time a headstone will be placed on the grave 
at the cicero cemetery 
