are dead some of them are tired and some of them are young 
plants 1990 tour kicks off in europe on may 1 and should be in 
the states shortly after 
im very lucky he said i have a particularly strong live 
following and i havent had huge top 40 hits but ive got a pretty 
big interested live following which is great its kind of 
greater than if id had top 40 hits and nothing else 
