planebuilding operations in california and georgia merged under 
one management 
the division has come on hard times of late with four major 
military plane programs ended or about to end the c5 cargo plane 
the p3 antisubmarine patrol plane the tr1 highaltitude 
reconnaisance plane and the f117a stealth fighter 
