<TEXT>
shedding nicknames like chateau de 
bubba and cowboy cabernet a west texas winery has proven 
beyond a sip of sauvignon that wine from the south plains can get 
some respect even from the french 
this month three labels from llano estacado winerys 
awardwinning stock have begun appearing in 350 restaurants in 
france 
