representative to the talks along with sens robert byrd dwva 
lloyd bentsen dtexas and james sasser dtenn the chairmen of 
appropriations finance and budget respectively 
senate minority leader dole named sen phil gramm rtexas as 
his representative with sens mark o hatfield rore bob 
packwood rore and pete v domenici rnm also of 
appropriations finance and budget 
the white house announced that in addition to bush who will 
sit in on the talks from time to time its negotiators would be 
budget director richard darman chief of staff john sununu and 
treasury secretary nicholas brady 
