the cost of living increased by 
114 percent in april sharply down from the previous months 955 
percent leap the economy ministry announced 
the april figure was the lowest monthly costofliving increase 
since last novembers 65 percent it left inflation over the 
previous 12 months at 169032 percent and 2518 percent for the 
year to date 
officials on wednesday attributed the sharp april decline to a 
severe antiinflationary adjustment to economic policy put into 
effect by the 10monthold government of president carlos menem 
planning secretary moises ikonicoff said the april decline 
confirmed a tendency toward stabilization initiated in the second 
half of march and predicted the may inflation rate would be even 
lower than aprils 
carlos carballo undersecretary of economy said the april 
decline in inflation indicated that public finances are under 
control a return to hyperinflation experienced from december 
through march is little short of impossible he added 
the cost of living rose 401 percent in december 792 percent 
in january and 616 percent in february the 12month inflation 
figure hit a high of 20266 percent in march 
in its recent policy adjustment the government sharply reduced 
the money supply halting the practice of printing money to finance 
deficit spending by public companies and other government entities 
earlier economy minister antonio ernan gonzalez removed 
exchange controls allowing the local currency to float against the 
dollar and sharply increased public utility rates and fuel prices 
menem a 59yearold lawyer and former provincial governor has 
pledged to spur economic growth by balancing the budget selling 
moneylosing state companies deregulating monopolies ending 
subsidies lowering trade barriers reforming the tax code and 
eliminating corruption 
economic policy has been criticized by organized labor which 
charges that real wages have fallen 50 percent below the average 
for the 1980s and claims that privatization will lead to loss of 
jobs and benefits as well as national patrimony 
